body:
#### PR description:

The goal of this PR is to address [CMSHLT-3299](https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/CMSHLT-3299) by cleaning up few bits of unused customizations in the `HLTrigger/Configuration` area:

1) `customizeHLTforAlpaka.py`: remove all customization, but keep the file for future developments
2) `customizeHLTforNewDatasetDefinition.py`: remove completely.
3) `customizeHLTforCMSSW.py`: remove the following functions:
```
def customiseHCALFor2018Input(prcess):
def customiseFor2017DtUnpacking(process):
def customisePixelGainForRun2Input(process):
def customisePixelL1ClusterThresholdForRun2Input(process):
def customiseCTPPSFor2018Input(process):
def customiseEGammaRecoFor2018Input(process):
def customiseBeamSpotFor2018Input(process):
def customiseECALCalibrationsFor2018Input(process):
def customiseFor2018Input(process):
def checkHLTfor43774(process):
```
4) `customizeHLTforMC.py`: remove its content completely but keep the file (it is called from various places in CMSSW).

#### PR validation:

`addOnTests.py` runs fine. No regressions are expected

#### If this PR is a backport please specify the original PR and why you need to backport that PR. If this PR will be backported please specify to which release cycle the backport is meant for:

Not a backport, will not be backported
